Right now our plan is 8CPU, 1GB RAM, for $40 + $10 backup.  If I simply have our system rebooted we'll end up at 2GB RAM for the same cost, which is overkill for our current load.  Switching to the lower plan will change our costs from $50/month to $30/month.<br />
